To release a new version:

* git tag 1.x.x
* git push --tags
* Update NovaSDK.podspec.json with new version (s.version and s.source)
* pod spec lint NovaSDK.podspec.json
* Correct any issues
* Commit and push

Then in clone of https://github.com/nova-device/Specs/:
* mkdir Specs/NovaSDK/1.x.x
* cp (podspec from this repo) to Specs/NovaSDK/1.x.x/
* commit, push and perform a pull request

